  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peace building and trauma healing in Unity State, South Sudan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This package is for funds towards a two year project, which aims to provide protection and psychosocial support to displaced and conflict-affected communities, as well as facilitating peacebuilding and reconciliation between IDPs and their host communities, in and around Kol, Pathiel and Nyandong payams within the Greater Nyal and Mayendit South regions of Unity, South Sudan. The project is majority funded by the Stanley Thomas Johnson Foundation.</narrative>
  </description>
